                            <comment id="15270168" author="yukim" created="Wed, 4 May 2016 06:10:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think this has been broken since we switched to use native driver in 2.2.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;BulkLoader.buildSSLOption&lt;/tt&gt; checks &lt;tt&gt;enabled&lt;/tt&gt; in client enc option but never is set.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch to set &lt;tt&gt;enabled&lt;/tt&gt; when either of those 4 options (-ts/-tspw/-ks/-kspw) is set.&lt;/p&gt;

